{
  "stem": "5626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And next year, when the memorial wall was put up in the town of Ujpest, in the yard of the synagogue, we went out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We thought that we are free person, and there will be no more word against the Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "As I mentioned, that the synagogue, the Conservative synagogue, was in the same street where I grew up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We walked through the street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "In the building we used to live, people were standing in the window, and looking down the street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I hear, from the same building where l live, somebody says, look at this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "More of them came back than left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was the last word which I kept in my mind until today, when I hear that more came back than left.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "If they would know, if they would be there at the march, if they would see the gas chamber inside, they would see the ovens.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they see the mound and mounds and mounds of dead body.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Which were naturally opened out after the concentration camp was-- in the four days I spend after the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --liberation over there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "The German soldiers who were rounded up, they had to open out these mass graves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they put body parts-- there were no whole body.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "You know, the lye melts the body [? of you ?] very fast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They were put in 60 kilogram in each potato sack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And that is a cemetery still, in the Gunskirchen forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I will jump now, a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Life started and life went on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We had our only child, born.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "He grew up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name is Steven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Hungarian he was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Pishdar, ?] And he was about 3 and 1/2 years old when we had the Hungarian Revolution.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
